{
  "stem": "142.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that means from January-- yeah, quite a few months there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And while you were in Melk, what were the conditions like there?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bad-- every condition is-- you know, we weren't used to such a cold weather-- very, very cold weather.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the only thing we survive is because working at the Sonderkommando, I was well nourished for the march.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And until there, you know, I was surviving, you know, even with very, very little food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That came about to the end of it when from Melk, I went to Ebensee, Austria, you know, in April 1945.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then in Ebensee, the work there was in-- in tunnels of-- in caves of mountains, moving stones of hundred, 200 pounds from one place to another.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The only thing they were waiting is to kill us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were-- we heard the rumors that they want to put us all in the caves, and then put a bomb and finish with us.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But they didn't succeeded, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But-- and it happens that one morning, you know, I just-- I get up, 5:30 or 6 o'clock in the morning, and there is such a silence-- silence, nothing, nobody.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Just-- just heard the birds singing, the only thing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, Ebensee is a beautiful tourist place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's one of the most beautiful places in Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And seeing around nobody, I come out-- no guards, nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So we come out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, there was nobody in the camp anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It took a couple of hours and the American army came in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we start crying, and crying, and crying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they start you know, taking care of us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And the only problem-- I think they were giving soups.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And soups-- it's-- a lot of people had diarrhea and they died.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
